Kamstrup acknowledges the increasing reliance on digital systems and cybersecurity to power its products and safeguard sensitive data, noting the intensified digital demands in recent years. The company aims to provide solutions that are accurate, reliable, and secure, as demonstrated in projects like the large-scale smart metering rollout in Ireland with Siemens."""
